{"tid":720093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【槍擊爭產】自稱係保鑣 但女疑犯冇槍牌冇保安牌？","createTime":"2018-06-27T16:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T16:58:04.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"911de28875c518946faa0281c7188c3686fc76ba","tid":720093,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"【槍擊爭產】自稱係保鑣 但女疑犯冇槍牌冇保安牌？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【23:40更新】根據保安及護衞業管理委員會備存的資料，「第一保鑣BodyGuard01」並不在香港持牌保安公司名單之內。<br />\n<br />\n太古城鰂魚涌公園昨日發生爭產開槍殺人案，女保鑣涉嫌槍擊兩舅父和兩阿姨，造成2死2傷(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lyuxpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lyuxpI&d=L9zDiJgvA7hBrz6iFPvoBmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=733f1d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lyuxpI</a>)，她仍然被警方扣留調查。早前她接受傳媒訪問時自稱是行內少數的女保鑣，為香港一間保鑣公司的負責人之一，但有消息稱，女疑犯未有槍牌也沒有保安牌照，而她昨日使用俗稱「掌心雷」的半自動手槍亦未有槍牌，至於疑犯經營的保鑣公司更沒有槍牌及保安牌照。<br />\n<br />\n警方在女疑犯家中搜出3支槍枝，經軍械鑪證專家檢查後，有兩支屬玩具槍，另外一支為氣槍，火力低於兩焦耳，而警員在現場進行地氈式搜索，亦尋回4粒彈殼，相信與案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n根據《火器及彈藥條例》，發槍牌條件包括要由槍會推薦、受專業訓練等。而任何人非法管有槍械或彈藥，最高可被判監十四年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180627/58370844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58370844&d=L9zDiJgvA7hBrz6iFPvoBmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4b3979b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58370844&h=f6783c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180627/58370844</a>f"},{"pid":"b4673b944940c7191eac027ac390bde4ddbf5a90","tid":720093,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c09d0e5d365102ee87f48fa9ee2fbda451c92bc","tid":720093,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"呢D先係炒車架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eac9452b9cc60f57ca3464112a5043c11707607","tid":720093,"uid":7402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629601f2ff4a736535dac3555cfbb462ba777f96","tid":720093,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"招搖撞騙  戅鳩老千"}]}